metadata.description:
This token represents an early investment share.  All capital from the first 10 shares are directly paying for all SEC fees / legal fees. Thousand Brokers is a private closed-end fund represented by 1000 investors. The fund is ran exactly like a DAO but is legally represented as a private equity fund regulated by the United States department of Securities and Exchange Commission. Each NFT represents a share in the revenue pool for all buying and selling of assets under the fund. Each share represents 1 vote out of 1000 total for every investing decision by the fund. 
Tokens #0001 - #0010  represents 0.002 or 0.2% of the profit pool per NFT . Tokens #0011 - #1000 represents 0.00102041 or 0.102041% of the profit pool per NFT. All investors have access to portfolio gains from the biggest projects on the decentralized NFT market. Fund manager - parkerxbtc
metadata.name: Investor Share #0001
